    "body": "I think part of the reason I didn't implement it initially was because it'd be unclear if the conditional formatting should be applied on just the first `n` rows, and then displayed, or whether the conditional formatting should be applied to the entire frame, and then the first `n` rows displayed.\r\n\r\n@aaronbarzilai I don't know if it works for your use-case, but you might want to investigate `Styler.export` and `Styler.use`: http://pandas-docs.github.io/pandas-docs-travis/style.html#Sharing-Styles"
